00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:19,880
But for families like ours,

578
00:25:20,140 --> 00:25:21,740
when looking for a marriage partner,

579
00:25:21,740 --> 00:25:23,520
we always hope
the other's family background

580
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,440
is not too far apart from ours.

581
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:28,480
Mom.

582
00:25:28,860 --> 00:25:30,960
Yao Yuan is gentle and caring,

583
00:25:31,180 --> 00:25:32,960
kind-hearted and optimistic.

584
00:25:33,140 --> 00:25:35,220
I believe she'll get along well

585
00:25:35,220 --> 00:25:37,080
with everyone.

586
00:25:38,340 --> 00:25:39,720
Is she really that great?

587
00:25:39,860 --> 00:25:42,160
You have to trust my judgment.

588
00:25:42,780 --> 00:25:43,800
I've met her a few times.

589
00:25:44,100 --> 00:25:45,720
She seems like a good girl.

590
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:49,880
I just don't know

591
00:25:50,100 --> 00:25:51,640
whether your father will approve.

592
00:25:52,740 --> 00:25:54,700
On your dad's birthday,

593
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:55,840
you need to arrive early.

594
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:57,800
Don't skip any of the proper etiquette.

595
00:25:58,340 --> 00:25:59,280
Also,

596
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:00,620
you have to make sure

597
00:26:00,620 --> 00:26:02,700
she dresses like a refined young lady

598
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:04,000
and shows up looking beautiful.

599
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:05,220
Got it?

600
00:26:05,220 --> 00:26:06,160
Sure.

601
00:26:12,100 --> 00:26:12,940
(Successful proposal)

602
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,920
(Official proposal)
Introduce her to the family.

603
00:26:23,540 --> 00:26:24,520
It's time

604
00:26:25,700 --> 00:26:27,320
to move this forward.

605
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:35,580
(Yuting: What a great couple.)

606
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,280
Your thoughts don't matter.

607
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:40,040
Others don't want to see this.

608
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,500
(Yuting: What a great couple.)

609
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:46,440
That's the little girl

610
00:26:46,440 --> 00:26:47,980
bravely chasing after love?

611
00:26:49,620 --> 00:26:51,260
I really don't get today's young girls.

612
00:26:51,260 --> 00:26:52,640
How can they be so shameless?

613
00:26:53,380 --> 00:26:54,680
Times really have changed.

614
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,180
What are you worried about?

615
00:26:57,180 --> 00:26:58,480
Wen Cheng doesn't even like her.

616
00:26:59,540 --> 00:27:01,280
But with an opponent like her...

617
00:27:04,420 --> 00:27:06,040
Are you afraid Wen Cheng might waver?

618
00:27:06,780 --> 00:27:08,260
What does it matter to me if he does?

619
00:27:10,140 --> 00:27:11,300
If you're scared he'll waver,

620
00:27:11,380 --> 00:27:12,620
go ask him.

621
00:27:12,620 --> 00:27:14,240
Sulking at home

622
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:15,400
won't change anything.

623
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:16,800
Look at her,

624
00:27:17,100 --> 00:27:18,920
young and stunning.

625
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:21,280
She's also very sweet.

626
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:23,240
What man wouldn't be tempted?

627
00:27:24,140 --> 00:27:24,860
Xinran,

628
00:27:24,860 --> 00:27:26,060
you're under so much pressure.

629
00:27:26,060 --> 00:27:27,760
Why not let Wen Cheng know?

630
00:27:29,900 --> 00:27:30,900
Honestly,

631
00:27:30,900 --> 00:27:32,120
this might be a good chance

632
00:27:32,900 --> 00:27:35,120
to let you realize
how much you care about him.

633
00:27:36,300 --> 00:27:37,680
Alright, now,

634
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:38,880
are you going to back out?

635
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:40,320
Or will you make a move?

636
00:27:40,780 --> 00:27:42,060
If I back out,

637
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,200
I won't be satisfied.

638
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:44,700
If I go all in,

639
00:27:44,700 --> 00:27:46,400
I'm afraid I'll end up getting hurt.

640
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:48,760
What should I do?

641
00:27:49,980 --> 00:27:51,060
- It's okay.
- Well.

642
00:27:51,540 --> 00:27:52,800
She's too young.

643
00:27:53,100 --> 00:27:54,160
Then you beat her.

644
00:27:57,100 --> 00:27:58,240
I'll poke her again.

645
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,500
You always forget to eat
when editing photos.

646
00:28:20,580 --> 00:28:21,780
I brought takeout and red wine.

647
00:28:23,300 --> 00:28:24,780
How did you know I was editing photos?

648
00:28:25,340 --> 00:28:27,120
If you didn't leave,
you must be working.

649
00:28:30,540 --> 00:28:31,640
Why won't you let me in?

650
00:28:31,900 --> 00:28:32,840
I'm not hungry.

651
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:36,220
I just remembered.

652
00:28:36,220 --> 00:28:37,620
I think I left some personal clothes

653
00:28:37,620 --> 00:28:38,840
at your place.

654
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,020
I guess you wouldn't want

655
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:42,020
your future girlfriend
to accidentally find them.

656
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:47,480
Grab them and leave.

657
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,080
What are you doing?

658
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,100
I'm hungry.

659
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:06,440
I'll leave after I finish eating.

660
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:13,730
♪It's too foggy to see the way♪

661
00:29:14,300 --> 00:29:18,670
♪I wish you were right here beside me♪

662
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:20,440
Why do you still not believe me?

663
00:29:20,940 --> 00:29:21,880
Believe what?

664
00:29:22,820 --> 00:29:24,400
That I want to get back with you.

665
00:29:26,500 --> 00:29:27,440
You're drunk.

666
00:29:28,060 --> 00:29:29,540
If you could walk in a straight line,

667
00:29:29,540 --> 00:29:30,640
- I'll consider...
- Fine.

668
00:29:31,420 --> 00:29:32,580
I'm not drunk.

669
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:34,320
I'll walk right now to prove it.

670
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:46,400
♪That day, we walked side by side
down the street♪

671
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:55,020
♪That day, your smiling face
lit up the world♪

672
00:29:55,060 --> 00:29:56,680
So, the TV drama was true.

673
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:57,940
Girls always fall

674
00:29:57,940 --> 00:29:59,640
right into the male lead's arms.

675
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:05,380
We're almost out of red wine.
I'll go get some.

676
00:30:05,380 --> 00:30:06,320
Hey.

677
00:30:06,820 --> 00:30:07,860
You're drunk.

678
00:30:07,860 --> 00:30:08,800
I'll go.

679
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:15,290
♪Someday, we'll say goodbye with grace♪

680
00:30:39,820 --> 00:30:40,660
(Log in)

681
00:30:50,220 --> 00:30:51,100
(Bestie)

682
00:30:51,100 --> 00:30:54,060
(Xiduomeng Tea Proposal Report)

683
00:31:03,900 --> 00:31:04,840
The coffee is ready.

684
00:31:07,260 --> 00:31:08,200
Ms. Wang,

685
00:31:08,420 --> 00:31:09,360
here's your coffee.

686
00:31:09,580 --> 00:31:10,960
Hey, Ms. Wang, your coffee.

687
00:31:14,580 --> 00:31:15,640
I'll get back to work now.

688
00:31:16,260 --> 00:31:17,200
Wait.

689
00:31:20,340 --> 00:31:21,280
This isn't what I want.

690
00:31:22,220 --> 00:31:23,400
I was very clear just now.

691
00:31:24,020 --> 00:31:25,200
Swap the milk for soy milk.

692
00:31:25,660 --> 00:31:27,080
Medium, no milk foam.

693
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:28,320
And add ice.

694
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:30,720
Which ear didn't catch that?

695
00:31:32,700 --> 00:31:33,940
But I remember...

696
00:31:33,940 --> 00:31:34,880
(Latte)
Exchange it.

697
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:36,520
You'll cover the cost yourself.

698
00:31:39,060 --> 00:31:40,320
I have a meeting soon.

699
00:31:40,330 --> 00:31:41,220
How about...

700
00:31:41,220 --> 00:31:42,480
Stop trying to shift the blame.

701
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,200
I'm telling you to go.

702
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:46,060
You can't even get coffee right.

703
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,440
How will you handle anything else?

704
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:02,320
Sorry about that.

705
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:13,640
What's going on?

706
00:32:15,260 --> 00:32:16,200
Mr. Jiang.

707
00:32:16,660 --> 00:32:18,340
A new hire

708
00:32:18,340 --> 00:32:19,560
can't do anything right.

709
00:32:20,820 --> 00:32:22,260
I accidentally slipped it,

710
00:32:22,260 --> 00:32:24,020
so it spilled. Sorry about that.

711
00:32:24,020 --> 00:32:25,000
Why are you apologizing?

712
00:32:26,820 --> 00:32:28,140
Let's go; it's nothing.

713
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:29,080
Boss.

714
00:32:30,180 --> 00:32:31,680
I have a question for you.

715
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:34,960
Why do you trust her so much?

716
00:32:38,500 --> 00:32:40,320
I don't know who recommended her.

717
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:41,880
But Boss,

718
00:32:42,060 --> 00:32:43,920
you've always been fair and impartial.

719
00:32:44,220 --> 00:32:45,360
So, I'll be straightforward.

720
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:48,020
She has

721
00:32:48,020 --> 00:32:49,640
no relevant experience,

722
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:51,620
yet you put her in charge
of a special project.

723
00:32:51,900 --> 00:32:53,440
You even have others support her.

724
00:32:54,740 --> 00:32:56,000
Is she threatening you?

725
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,040
No.

726
00:32:58,380 --> 00:32:59,480
I just can't stand her

727
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:00,620
relying on your backing

728
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:01,840
while doing nothing.

729
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,580
I'm worried she might slack off,

730
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:05,920
so I'm just training her.

731
00:33:07,020 --> 00:33:08,300
I heard you asked her

732
00:33:08,300 --> 00:33:10,120
to help your team organize the files

733
00:33:10,620 --> 00:33:11,820
and go alone to the warehouse

734
00:33:11,820 --> 00:33:12,760
to move heavy stuff.

735
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:14,440
Is that so?

736
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,800
What's the big deal?

737
00:33:16,100 --> 00:33:17,240
Every one of us

738
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:18,960
has been through tough times like that.

739
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:20,300
So, her hand got hurt

740
00:33:20,300 --> 00:33:21,240
because of you?

741
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,140
You went to complain about me?

742
00:33:26,220 --> 00:33:27,160
Huh?

743
00:33:27,580 --> 00:33:28,680
I was just waiting to see

744
00:33:29,220 --> 00:33:30,920
when you'd bring the boss in.

745
00:33:32,340 --> 00:33:33,280
Ms. Wang,

746
00:33:34,540 --> 00:33:36,160
from today, go home and rest.

747
00:33:37,780 --> 00:33:40,360
Finish handing over your tasks
before you leave.

748
00:33:41,180 --> 00:33:42,160
Go home and think

749
00:33:42,820 --> 00:33:44,520
about why you did all this.

750
00:33:45,580 --> 00:33:47,840
Given how much you've contributed
to the company,

751
00:33:47,980 --> 00:33:49,320
I'm not firing you outright.

752
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,320
When you think it through,

753
00:33:52,220 --> 00:33:53,260
you can come back to work.

754
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:56,400
Boss.

755
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,680
Is it only because of her?

756
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:03,640
My company

757
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:06,000
does not tolerate workplace bullying.

758
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,460
Having skills

759
00:34:07,470 --> 00:34:09,460
doesn't give you the right
to pick on newcomers.

760
00:34:10,220 --> 00:34:11,160
Besides,

761
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:13,780
the person you're bullying

762
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:15,520
belongs to me.

763
00:34:16,380 --> 00:34:17,460
Do I need to explain more?

764
00:34:26,980 --> 00:34:28,620
This time, our collaboration with Yike

765
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:29,920
is a new kind of project.

766
00:34:30,460 --> 00:34:33,240
It combines photographers
with advertising proposals.

767
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:34,420
If it goes well,

768
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:35,640
we can also pitch annual plans

769
00:34:35,640 --> 00:34:36,520
to manufacturers.

770
00:34:36,700 --> 00:34:37,580
So, this battle

771
00:34:37,580 --> 00:34:38,600
is crucial.

772
00:34:42,380 --> 00:34:43,520
Thank you for your hard work.

773
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,240
Today,

774
00:34:45,740 --> 00:34:47,440
I have a personal announcement to make.

775
00:34:51,420 --> 00:34:52,600
From now on,

776
00:34:53,060 --> 00:34:55,020
please stop guessing or speculating

777
00:34:55,020 --> 00:34:56,320
about my love life.

778
00:34:56,660 --> 00:34:57,820
I want to be upfront and share

779
00:34:58,740 --> 00:34:59,660
that Yao Yuan

780
00:34:59,940 --> 00:35:00,860
is my girlfriend.

781
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,420
I didn't make this public before

782
00:35:06,540 --> 00:35:08,380
because I didn't want anyone to feel

783
00:35:08,380 --> 00:35:09,640
there was any unfair treatment.

784
00:35:10,020 --> 00:35:11,100
Now that I'm sharing this,

785
00:35:11,340 --> 00:35:13,380
it's to avoid any baseless rumors.

786
00:35:13,820 --> 00:35:15,300
Such rumors only hurt Yao Yuan

787
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:17,300
and cause me unnecessary trouble.

788
00:35:18,020 --> 00:35:18,980
That said,

789
00:35:18,980 --> 00:35:20,420
work is work.

790
00:35:21,180 --> 00:35:22,100
You

791
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:23,380
don't need

792
00:35:23,700 --> 00:35:25,060
to treat Yao Yuan differently.

793
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:31,020
A real rags-to-riches story.

794
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:32,700
Yeah, Ms. Wang

795
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:34,380
stepped into some serious trouble.

796
00:35:50,900 --> 00:35:51,820
Yeah.

797
00:35:53,020 --> 00:35:54,500
Do you want to go, too?

798
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:55,620
I need someone for lighting.

799
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,260
Remember the self-defense technique

800
00:35:58,260 --> 00:35:59,280
I taught you last night?

801
00:35:59,380 --> 00:36:00,540
You can't let your guard down

802
00:36:00,540 --> 00:36:01,660
against this man.

803
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:04,940
Are you jealous again?

804
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:06,700
Didn't you say
in the meeting to keep work

805
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:07,760
and personal life separate?

806
00:36:07,940 --> 00:36:09,020
I'll make sure of it.

807
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:11,500
But now, we're not at the company.

808
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:15,340
Hey, I'm also here.

809
00:36:20,620 --> 00:36:21,900
Hurry up.

810
00:36:32,460 --> 00:36:33,380
Don't smile.

811
00:36:44,870 --> 00:36:45,660
Alright, everyone.

812
00:36:45,660 --> 00:36:47,060
That's a wrap for today's shooting.

813
00:36:47,060 --> 00:36:48,140
Thanks for participating.

814
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:50,460
We'll treat you to something delicious.

815
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:51,820
Mr. Su.

816
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:53,380
We'd love to take a photo with you.

817
00:36:53,540 --> 00:36:54,460
Sure.

818
00:36:54,620 --> 00:36:55,540
Of course.

819
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,040
Let's take a picture with you.

820
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:58,160
Let's snap a photo.

821
00:36:58,940 --> 00:36:59,780
Look this way.

822
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,220
Thank you so much.

823
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,580
This time, thanks to you,

824
00:37:11,940 --> 00:37:13,380
I finished the Bestie Project.

825
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:15,620
You're so dedicated.

826
00:37:16,450 --> 00:37:17,700
Is it because of Jiang?

827
00:37:25,060 --> 00:37:26,140
Look at those students.

828
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,740
They deserve to be just like them.

829
00:37:29,620 --> 00:37:30,540
In life,

830
00:37:30,780 --> 00:37:32,020
everyone should have a bestie,

831
00:37:32,580 --> 00:37:33,500
a confidant.

832
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:35,740
So, are we

833
00:37:36,260 --> 00:37:37,220
besties?

834
00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:39,620
You're overthinking it.

835
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:41,140
We're not quite there yet.

836
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:44,300
But

837
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:46,220
we do have something in common.

838
00:37:48,220 --> 00:37:49,060
We're both trying

839
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:50,020
to prove ourselves.

840
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:51,820
I want to prove

841
00:37:52,460 --> 00:37:54,180
that I can be Anlan's right-hand.

842
00:37:55,700 --> 00:37:56,780
You're proving

843
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,900
you haven't lost yourself

844
00:37:58,900 --> 00:37:59,920
in your creative journey.

845
00:38:01,260 --> 00:38:02,580
So, in a way,

846
00:38:02,580 --> 00:38:03,500
we're comrades?

847
00:38:05,140 --> 00:38:06,060
You could say that.

848
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:07,380
Best comrades.

849
00:38:09,140 --> 00:38:10,060
Honestly,

850
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,100
it's the first time I've heard a woman

851
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:13,260
describe me like that.

852
00:38:13,900 --> 00:38:15,380
Looks like my charm

853
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:17,260
has dropped below passing.

854
00:38:19,500 --> 00:38:20,420
But Yao Yuan,

855
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:22,740
thanks to you,

856
00:38:22,940 --> 00:38:24,460
I found my inspiration again

857
00:38:26,650 --> 00:38:27,820
and slowly rediscovered

858
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:29,920
the original purpose behind photography.

859
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:43,030
What do you think?

860
00:38:43,490 --> 00:38:44,340
My work should meet

861
00:38:44,340 --> 00:38:46,180
your company's requirements, right?

862
00:38:48,820 --> 00:38:50,380
Does Su Wen know you're here?

863
00:38:51,900 --> 00:38:52,820
He doesn't.

